  "content": {
    "headline": "We put everything we are into everything we do",
    "tagline": "A global creative company",
    "valueProps": [
      "VML is a global creative company that believes the most powerful way to drive growth is by creating connected brands.",
      "We bring this to life by seamlessly connecting Brand Experience, Customer Experience, and Commerce, always thinking about the entire journey a person has with a brand — from first impression to purchase and beyond.",
      "By blending our award-winning creativity with deep technical expertise, we offer something unique — the vision of a creative agency with the power of a technology consultancy.",
      "Our 26,000 talented people across the globe provide the local insights and worldwide scale to develop ideas that matter and that create impact for our partners.",
      "When you put human connection at the heart of a brand, it doesn’t just grow — it thrives."
    ],
    "tone": "Confident, human-centric, and ambitious. Blends creative-agency warmth with technology-consultancy authority; emphasizes connection, scale, growth, and craft. Corporate but aspirational (© 2026 VML, A WPP Company)."
